msgid "Bangladeshi"
msgstr "방글라데시인"

#: data/nation/bangladeshi.ruleset:4
msgid "?plural:Bangladeshis"
msgstr "방글라데시인"

#: data/nation/bangladeshi.ruleset:6
msgid "The People's Republic of Bangladesh was formed from the former Pakistani territory of East Bengal following a war of independence."
msgstr "방글라데시 인민공화국은 독립 전쟁 뒤 옛 파키스탄 영토였던 동벵골에서 형성되었습니다."

